messages.messageBody:
In response to "dancing the dance" with my husband before. My belief
is the same as yours. You know if you've know someone before or
not. Deja vu.......part of the blueprint that your on track.

I had thousands of questions until everyone of them was answered in a
book by Sylvia Brown called "The other side and back". May sound
hokey to some people but "religion" could never answer any of them.
A friend of mine had to push the book down my throat.....I thought
she was so silly. Now I am so at the final understanding.

Crystal
